snippet.title: Amber Tries To Get Her Case Dismissed For The Third Time!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Tries To Get A Case Dismissal For The Third Time Now

✅ Like & Subscribe for more Celebrity Content!

Just when people thought Amber Heard's bizarre attempts to get away with her injustices during her relationship with acclaimed actor Johnny Depp were nearing an end, she goes even lower. Her lawsuit with Johnny was recently rejected for the third time by the judges, after consistently asking for a case dismissal. But as it seems the judges aren't having it as they have rejected Amber's legal team's appeal for the third time now! But what really happened? Are the Virginia judges seriously considering Amber's legal team's move? 

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
